Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:57.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(185,100)\fs20}迷 途 貓  搭 乘 了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散落在廣袤宇宙中的點點繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中  住有生命體的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,則是少之又少
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這蔚藍的  閃耀著的美麗的地球也是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡一般的幾率之下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球孕育出了成千上萬種生物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並延續了數十億年的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  有三個能源生命體正降落到地球上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是從Brave星球而來的三位勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.62,0:00:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了從企圖支配全宇宙的機械帝國的魔掌下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護地球的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們現在還不停地戰鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:15.31,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才不是什麼膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:20.95,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不知道怎麼使用勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:24.49,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直守候在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:28.99,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅信著會有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.66,0:01:33.25,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從朦朧的夢中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:36.09,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把愛找出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:39.21,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無可取代的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:42.93,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要誓死守護著 絕不閉上雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:52.39,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Braver  翱翔天際吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:57.90,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所向無敵 張開翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:03.61,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Braver  用彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:09.49,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把巨大的V字 刻在心底裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.79,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(230,350)}SAY!YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:12.79,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FLYING!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:12.79,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(415,350)}Make waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:19.88,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1800)}Grand Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙也加她們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.97,0:02:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要幹這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了向機械帝國復仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙也加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:37.42,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}覺醒之光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙也加她們把你當成朋友看待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救助朋友  這是永恆不變的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就看穿你要背叛我們機械帝國了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說要回帝國一陣子  那是騙我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪惡的叛亂分子看來也來齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  它想要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  但千萬別大意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些Brave星的死剩種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以通過融合地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使力量成倍成倍地增強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對此我已經調查過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械公爵它一直在研究這個迷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把那個謎團的其中一部分解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜大眼睛看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面被機械公爵吸了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…它正在跟大地…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…跟地球融合！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那種東西打
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪還有勝算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:06:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有敵人的能量在不斷上升呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在吸取地球的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一刻我等了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快我就能獲得超越機械皇帝的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後有朝一日就能成為第二個機械皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…一個新的機械帝國的王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全宇宙的霸者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的野心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是即將降臨的現實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看著螢幕發現了點線索
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙也加妹妹的反應正逐漸變弱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙也加妹妹她們會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她們救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:06:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這幫劣種
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼亂七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經刻不容緩了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來作掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們可撐不了多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去把沙也加妹妹她們…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們很快就會回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  能聽到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會告訴你們  怎麼到沙也加妹妹她們那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了這個地步  就算把實驗體搶了回去也無關痛癢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Battler
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回應我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Battler
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是無能為力的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就待在那兒看著你的好朋友怎麼死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實在太無力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙也加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你也該懂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗機械帝國是什麼個下場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙也加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙也加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老是這麼慢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一醒來就說這種話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  忍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起  輪到我們反擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再凶也只是垂死掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只憑你們  事到如今還能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀掉了Brave Kaiser的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還毀掉了葉月她們的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙也加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還想連地球也毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些機械帝國的大壞蛋  罪無可恕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說的話  你全都替我說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我和沙也加的心情也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你瞧瞧我們的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brave Kaiser  Mach  Drill
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的精神信號值都突破了極限
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,325)\fs17}Soul  Signal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  來合體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人合體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者超人  Grand Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  儘管來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一鼓作氣  衝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Blade！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Attack！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Attack被…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把火焰吸走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這點本事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼弱還囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去掩護Grand Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  因為剛才的攻擊和墜落時的毀損
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有武器都無法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就在痛苦掙扎中去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只是被人保護著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法救出重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會一味的逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要  能拯救大家的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  這束光是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  這是共鳴之光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新的合體之光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  我們和葉月的機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠合體？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Braver和Big Battler步調一致
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員的精神信號值都突破了極限
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,325)\fs17}Soul  Signal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把機械公爵打飛掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打飛掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  集合大家的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來合體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行嗎  葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  只要能打倒機械公爵的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新·超人合體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:18:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武裝勇者  Great Grand Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛者和弱者加在一起  又能搞出什麼名堂來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也就是些劣種
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  生氣的可是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著鐵鞋踐踏別人的家園
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞得雞犬不寧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為我們會就這麼放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來幾次都是一樣的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法吸收  這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Charge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成為新的機械皇帝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事我才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我去死兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.27,0:20:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你了  葉月  助我們一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這次而已  我這麼做只是為了自己罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是討厭和我們親近呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能成我們的夥伴的話  一定很靠得住的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上這麼說  博士你其實只不過是想研究她的機體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那機體好像還包含了不少未知科學技術
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.11,0:21:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
